433
00:37:22,720 --> 00:37:25,580
These people all disappeared on the sixth day of May

434
00:37:25,720 --> 00:37:28,050
and returned two days later on the eighth.

435
00:37:29,880 --> 00:37:32,480
Just like what happened in Dengzhou this time.

436
00:37:32,760 --> 00:37:34,240
Except all these people...

437
00:37:34,240 --> 00:37:35,240
